jilles      2007/01/27 13:22:02 UTC	(23517)
  Log:
  Make NOBALLOC have the regular blockheap functions fall back
  to ircd_malloc()/ircd_free(), instead of using #defines. This
  ensures NOBALLOC does not change the ABI.
  

